Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了   请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要继续咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肉棒好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要继续咯  可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我   我把内衣脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.96,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧   要摸就摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.70,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你你很舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我   一起进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡鸡好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗   宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.83,0:07:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超好吃的耶   不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.56,0:10:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样    舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.96,0:10:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时问还很多     不要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.10,0:10:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么    我继续咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.36,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站好，我会害羞耶\N是这样呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你很爽好不好呢\N我很害羞啦！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.56,0:12:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何    还可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮你按摩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.83,0:16:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应真可爱呢   不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服不是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你乳交咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.90,0:21:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.83,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要慢慢动~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.23,0:23:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要继续呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.96,0:23:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很爽吧    我知道的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.10,0:23:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好爽   我还要~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.50,0:25:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好深入     你好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.16,0:26:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动   我自己来~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.30,0:31:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧    我帮你吹吹~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.56,0:32:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好我是JULIA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.16,0:32:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材真好呢   不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.23,0:32:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦     不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.56,0:32:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.36,0:32:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我摸摸    不好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.36,0:32:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱    不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:02.70,0:33:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢    没了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.63,0:33:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的反应哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.90,0:33:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超爽的    我哪好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:03.76,0:34:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要继续了    感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.03,0:35:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次好不好~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:19.90,0:35:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗   宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.43,0:35:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要   你脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.70,0:35:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱   身材不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.63,0:36:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么       我又要开始嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.03,0:36:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪好意思     想要我摸哪边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:19.36,0:36:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸这边好不好   可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.03,0:36:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太害羞了    不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.23,0:36:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个方式吧   可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.90,0:37:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈    看不到吧\N我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:01.50,0:37:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要脱掉咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.56,0:37:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.50,0:37:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧    我很认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:26.96,0:37:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌        很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:30.30,0:37:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很舒服吧    不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.83,0:37:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.76,0:38:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么    就脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.83,0:39:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的奶头更硬了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.76,0:39:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裤子脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.16,0:39:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.56,0:39:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我要干嘛吧~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.63,0:40:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶头真可爱    当然的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.50,0:40:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽       当然呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:36.96,0:40:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没摸了吧   我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:51.10,0:40:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺好   我帮你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.23,0:41:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧   我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.70,0:42:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更硬了   是呀..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.70,0:43:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽       你超强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.70,0:44:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要吗   恩！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.76,0:44:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽       你超棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:27.90,0:45:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换姿势吧   可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.36,0:46:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样呢       很舒服...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.03,0:46:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的呀    不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.10,0:47:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服      超棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:25.63,0:47:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样呢    是不是很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.76,0:48:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好敏感~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:18.56,0:49:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次吧   好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:46.56,0:49:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好爽   感激！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:51.36,0:50:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:05.63,0:51:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.90,0:51:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了    真的很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:54.56,0:51:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽        有够爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.10,0:52:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了   好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:33.76,0:52:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽       感谢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:08.83,0:53:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.76,0:53:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要放鸽子啦    怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:17.36,0:53:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊喔       快想办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:23.90,0:53:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个是打给我吗\N恩   是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.30,0:53:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到很久了呀       是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:40.43,0:53:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小间呢    对f呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:42.30,0:53:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邵没兴趣了  这样呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:52.83,0:53:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦      还满有情调的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.63,0:54:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想干嘛\N有什么打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:12.70,0:54:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:20.43,0:54:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好瘦   当然呀\N这是一-定要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:26.56,0:54:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好正   又好瘦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:32.43,0:54:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还蛮需要你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.50,0:54:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么办呢\N你觉得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:54.30,0:54:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很不好意思耶   不会啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:07.76,0:55:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面吗    是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:16.56,0:55:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我上你吧    好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:24.30,0:55:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认真耶        可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:31.10,0:55:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好色    你打算怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:38.03,0:55:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色哟    真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.50,0:55:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇     有各种价目表耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.36,0:55:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:52.96,0:55:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都好    看你要不要用呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:58.96,0:56:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀        我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:02.30,0:56:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看吧  好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:22.96,0:56:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的还蛮小间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:29.63,0:56:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.23,0:56:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么靠近    过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:38.43,0:56:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这样       我需要你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:47.90,0:56:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:04.70,0:57:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对    就是这样吧~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:10.30,0:57:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么    我要开始咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:22.96,0:57:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以用道具吗   可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:28.70,0:57:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗    好啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:33.50,0:57:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦      你要脱也可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:28.56,0:58:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掏出来呀   快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:01.90,0:59:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以舔吗   亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:32.83,0:59:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好正点   当然耶为你准备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:56.96,1:00:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗    当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:03.50,1:00:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拿来玩吗    好呀耶我都可以    没差啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.43,1:00:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看你胸部吗\N好呀   当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:21.90,1:00:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么    我们快继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:35.50,1:00:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要脱掉咯   好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:43.36,1:00:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好正    真的很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:15.76,1:01:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看吗   应该可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.23,1:01:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脱掉咯   好！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.96,1:01:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太害羞了     哪好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.50,1:02:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想上我吗     亲爱的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:29.23,1:02:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么靠近啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:48.56,1:02:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太害羞了    我说真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:10.30,1:03:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对   不要停
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:20.43,1:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要   我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:31.50,1:03:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真变态那\N我想要看你更实态
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:44.16,1:03:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个吧    好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:52.43,1:03:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然好     那就来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:58.16,1:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿了     不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:01.63,1:05:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗   宝贝\N想继续吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:23.10,1:05:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇    超硬的\N这到底该怎怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:30.96,1:05:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想一下\N应该有更好玩的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:38.16,1:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你吹好了   当然好！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:08.30,1:06:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快    来给我~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:09.76,1:07:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到你这样耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:17.23,1:07:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办   快射给我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.70,1:07:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大根   真的不错那
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:31.23,1:08:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很爽吧   是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:49.50,1:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了   不能上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:53.10,1:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没爱爱了\N拜托啦    求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:01.63,1:09:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我舔    我可以加价的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:52.70,1:09:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摸的活\N又要加价了耶~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:04.70,1:10:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦   不然你帮我舔奶就头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:28.70,1:10:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:57.63,1:11:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射给我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.76,1:11:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.43,1:11:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行   我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.76,1:11:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就好   拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:30.03,1:11:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要加钱喔   可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:42.16,1:11:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦    我选最贵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:47.63,1:11:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的唷  对啦\N我付得起的   好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:55.10,1:11:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧   我很期待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.76,1:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你要穿什么勾引我   好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.70,1:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手特别的\N好啦   我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:29.90,1:12:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿哪一件呀\N真是的   该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:35.76,1:12:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹啦   讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:03.23,1:13:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害羞耶   不会啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:09.10,1:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿就是了   不要闹啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:19.23,1:13:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好看   不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.96,1:13:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像穿反了耶\N换过来来好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:41.90,1:13:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真好看    不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:49.90,1:13:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒   超正的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:02.96,1:14:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太出羞了   我的天呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:22.16,1:14:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样呢   想看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:28.30,1:14:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠    会有感觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:31.90,1:14:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看奶头   好啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:41.63,1:14:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以舔吗    宝贝\N舔你的水蜜桃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:48.70,1:14:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸吧    好啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:06.30,1:15:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞        我这该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:20.56,1:15:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真变态    不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:40.16,1:15:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行     好痒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:11.36,1:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽    不能这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:10.16,1:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:28.83,1:17:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很爽吧   我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:00.16,1:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越轨了   不可以~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:04.43,1:18:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了   我不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:44.43,1:19:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边不可以~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:43.36,1:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很爽  说呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:18.70,1:23:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放进去了   怎么办！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:13.63,1:24:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸吗  宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:35.76,1:25:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:38.43,1:25:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超棒的好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:28.83,1:27:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧   不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:45.36,1:27:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要   拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:56.56,1:27:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了  你超棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:08.70,1:29:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔干净  快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:28.56,1:29:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  你都射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:57.10,1:29:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:18.56,1:30:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:37.50,1:30:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是私人招待所\N请你稍待片刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:47.36,1:30:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去请她出来     好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:09.90,1:31:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:12.03,1:31:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是请你喝的茶\N好的   谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:19.90,1:31:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:25.36,1:31:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么   可以在你旁边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:34.30,1:31:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:38.16,1:31:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦   忍不住吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:47.10,1:31:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦   不开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:55.36,1:31:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我皮肤很好摸的\N这样呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:01.76,1:32:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗   恩恩\N是真的还不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:08.83,1:32:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他人吗  嗯\N别担心~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:20.16,1:32:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你超可爱的    我好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:28.83,1:32:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之   让你开心好不好\N当然好呀   客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:38.43,1:32:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算怎么做呢\N说说看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:45.63,1:32:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心遇见你\N我也这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:59.76,1:33:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要沉默呀  真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:08.56,1:33:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是要给我一点点时间呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:18.43,1:33:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲一个好不好\N不会被看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:25.23,1:33:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦   要听话喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:37.76,1:33:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好软   超好摸的\N你好温柔呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:51.50,1:33:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想摸就摸吧    好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.10,1:34:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错呀   我说真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:25.36,1:34:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了   我好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:41.36,1:34:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好摸了  我说真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:04.96,1:35:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大    超棒的奶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:08.43,1:35:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想多看一点吗\N当然好  我还要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:15.76,1:35:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉红色的耶   好美！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:26.03,1:35:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不错\N就是说呀   喜欢是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:46.03,1:35:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摸摸看吗\N亲爱的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:06.96,1:36:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心嘛   亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:33.23,1:36:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好摸   你真的很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:19.36,1:37:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摸就摸吧   我不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:33.36,1:37:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好软   触感超好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:16.70,1:38:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摸就摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:26.70,1:38:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边要脱掉吗  先不要~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:57.36,1:38:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了    你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:14.56,1:39:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好色~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:16.30,1:40:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想上你喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:23.23,1:41:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒股吧  我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:39.23,1:41:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想舔哦   可以吗\N拜托你啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:59.63,1:42:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要摸内棒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:28.16,1:42:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧   我要开动了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:34.83,1:43:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦一下对吧   是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:53.63,1:46:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来吧    好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:40.70,1:48:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽       你超棒的I
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:03.36,1:51:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:39.76,1:51:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要不要呢  宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:28.83,1:52:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你射胸部上了耶\N来  我帮你舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:18.03,1:53:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有爽吗   恩恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:30.56,1:53:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空还要来哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:33.76,1:53:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好    我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:38.70,1:53:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来时\N让你体验更爽的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:11.90,1:54:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思   我要预约
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:21.10,1:54:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对    我在旅馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:00.43,1:55:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:06.03,1:55:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好   我是来帮你服务的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:15.50,1:55:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话\N我要开始咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:23.36,1:55:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:27.10,1:55:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你打电话的吧\N是呀   没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:37.10,1:55:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  你能帮我吗\N当然  没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:46.30,1:55:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  有我在\N我会想办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:55.50,1:56:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次耶\N不知道  表现得好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:04.83,1:56:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样呀  其实\N你不需要想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:14.96,1:56:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦   当然\N你真的有够可爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:27.36,1:56:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思耶   不会啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:38.43,1:56:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心   没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:48.70,1:56:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们慢慢来    不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:02.16,1:57:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了    不会啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:06.83,1:57:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么   直接开始吧\N没问题的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:16.30,1:57:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想怎么样都可以的   知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:28.16,1:57:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗    当然好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:19.63,1:58:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边搞吧   好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:43.23,2:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要继续咯  可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:04.83,2:02:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过样好兴奋  真的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:41.10,2:02:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:15.63,2:04:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽   超棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:43.90,2:06:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个资势吧    好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:36.83,2:07:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:57.63,2:07:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:57.63,2:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真好    真的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:02.83,2:09:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:14.16,2:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想多看一点吗   是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:39.63,2:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我上！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:07.10,2:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想上我吗    我都好~
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:14.70,2:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗  当然咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:23.10,2:14:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没差    我都有准备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:36.03,2:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会更爽的   知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:02.43,2:16:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的  放进去好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:56.56,2:16:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽   你超强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:02.56,2:17:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好   换个姿势势~
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:55.63,2:18:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住  可以射出来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:07.90,2:18:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽    这是当然的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:31.36,2:18:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好坏    想偷偷放进去耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:37.10,2:18:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕我忍不住\N你知道吗  宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:52.83,2:18:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偷偷放进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:00.83,2:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了   都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:11.10,2:19:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的    你好色\N都偷偷的欺负我
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:26.70,2:19:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪好意思  我的天呀\N你这坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:37.63,2:19:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管  我还要
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:47.90,2:19:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色哦   怎么这样呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:12.96,2:20:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等       不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:16.83,2:20:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉进去了\N不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:25.63,2:20:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行     会很爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:35.36,2:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好棒   我不要\N你够了啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:55.50,2:20:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:04.30,2:21:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽 天呀\N有够紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:55.63,2:22:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:05.50,2:23:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗   宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:09.23,2:23:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超爽的   真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:07.50,2:24:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何    还要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:15.36,2:25:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗  嗯\N超棒的  好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:35.63,2:25:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干死我吧   拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:17.23,2:27:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽   天呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:19.36,2:28:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射超多的   我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:23.23,2:28:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛时脸上   忍不住呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:23.10,2:29:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦    谢谢你\N你真的很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:32.03,2:29:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再找我吧   当然好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:48.56,2:29:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了   里面请
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:00.30,2:30:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:01.90,2:33:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行j啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:14.16,2:50:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射很多呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:50:22.03,2:50:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:51:06.83,2:51:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都滴出来了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:51:16.96,2:51:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次还要来知道吗
