Dialogue: Marked=0,3:05:39.36,3:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很爽   说说看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:06:33.76,3:06:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没差啦   放轻松就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:06:54.30,3:07:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好  换个方式\N我们继续吧
